<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend REST client doesn't will not work if you use query args in your URL.  This can be traced back to Zend_Uri_Http.</p>

<p>Example of a REST request that will fail:</p>

<p><a href="http://www.example.com/users/1?foo=bar">http://www.example.com/users/1?foo=bar</a></p>

<p>Once you remove the query arg, all is well.</p>

